# 1. Generate secrets and fill values above (JWT_SECRET, passwords, etc.)
# 2. docker compose up -d
# 3. docker logs nexora-whatsapp (scan QR)
# 4. http://localhost:8000/admin
# 5. Frontend should use http://localhost:8000/api for API calls
